{"tid":1395201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港首家快閃五金店上線啦 － 國難五金","createTime":"2019-08-01T16:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T07:51:38.000Z","uid":296349,"like":108,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1681c249d90f444c7604cc2046a25a3cb83e39","tid":1395201,"uid":296349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:21:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群來自民間的惡德商人，有鑑於最近香港局勢動盪，我們看到商機，決定借此機會發國難財，大賺一筆！<br />\n因此，我們的首家快閃五金店 － 「國難五金」正式上線，專營銷售各式頭盔、防護面具等保護用品。為慶祝國難五金正式開幕，新張期內將會有優惠套裝出售，並設有褔袋贈送給特定客人，客人入夜後有需要亦可於店內稍作休息。<br />\n<br />\n店舖：國難五金<br />\n營業時間：3/8 11:00 － 售完即止<br />\n地址：旺角道21號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GONazy6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGONazy6.jpg&h=5df6ba44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們貨真價實，童叟無欺，歡迎各位光臨選購。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VtdQzuQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVtdQzuQ.jpg&h=a08d17e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f2fe6a78af81c1ca16db41e3f4f2eb2f6990e3a","tid":1395201,"uid":45206,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"真？<br />\n又幾有生意頭腦"},{"pid":"619607dc724c1c0b8e345555e31eaca90b4bbfce","tid":1395201,"uid":6801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:30:16.000Z","msg":"光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4810db7f3b7c4902dcd11029b386ebe42ab20c","tid":1395201,"uid":235021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:30:47.000Z","msg":"想入股"},{"pid":"20f9e027f797f30f31a4286d67d5cddfbf47c8e1","tid":1395201,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":29,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"發死人財，大家負評就算，唔好推"},{"pid":"ec6860564f089caa4c6367971d663d215d923f69","tid":1395201,"uid":42767,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:31:31.000Z","msg":"黑警九成上黎cum檔"},{"pid":"99c4cfb8166c388a931fb4d85ae70e57dd8af329","tid":